{
  "stem": "1736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 399.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what they were going to do, but they were going to free them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe they were going to start shooting with broomsticks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- they deported them to the Isle of Man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they sat there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when Germany really looked, and in fact made an attempt to invade England, and that got too-- these people got too dangerous for the English to keep there, they decided to divide them up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by that time, there were about 3,000 or more prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they split them up into two ships.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One, I believe, went to Canada and was sunk, and the other one was sent to Australia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a troop ship, or converted troop ship, called the Dunera, and that is a separate story.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's been a film made about the Dunera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's a memorial here in Sydney to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's a Dunera Association.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was one of the Dunera boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he arrived in Sydney and was then sent to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hay, ?] to Tura.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sat out-- not sat out the war years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was there for a couple of years, and then they were given jobs in the armaments industry or whatever, you know, help they could do-- factories.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what he did for he last-- till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this is just a by-the-way story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the important part there is that during that time, he got to hear from my late mother that I had arrived in Palestine, as it was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we'll come back to that--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, there was contact with my mother through the Red Cross and also all the mail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, every letter was opened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
